<section id="about" class="py-24 px-6">
	<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
		<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">
			About<span class="text-[var(--color-accent)]">.</span>
		</h2>
		<div class="w-12 h-1 bg-[var(--color-accent)] rounded mb-10"></div>

		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
			<div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-5 text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
				<p>
					I'm a developer who enjoys turning complex problems into simple, elegant solutions.
					I focus on building applications that are performant, maintainable, and user-friendly.
				</p>
				<p>
					My professional journey began outside software development, where I spent several years working in the 3D animation industry. That experience taught me how to collaborate in multidisciplinary teams, solve complex problems, and continuously adapt to new challenges.

					After completing my training in web development and software engineering, I'm now focused on building my career as a developer. I've worked on both frontend and backend projects, and rather than specializing too early, I'm eager to explore different areas of software development and keep expanding my skills.

					I'm passionate about learning, improving every day, and creating software that is both reliable and enjoyable to use.
				</p>
				<p>

				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="space-y-4">
				<div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-surface)] border border-[var(--color-border)]">
					<p class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Location</p>
					<p class="text-white text-sm">Spain</p>
				</div>
				<div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-surface)] border border-[var(--color-border)]">
					<p class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Focus</p>
					<p class="text-white text-sm">Full-Stack Development</p>
				</div>
				<div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-surface)] border border-[var(--color-border)]">
					<p class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Interests</p>
					<p class="text-white text-sm">Data, Analytics, Gaming</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
